flowchart LR
    S["Wear the strap + wet electrodes"]
    S --> A["Scan and find the intended H10"]
    A --> B["Connect and validate the link"]
    B --> C["Confirm HR + ACC are moving"]
    C --> D["Inspect live ECG / ACC / RR"]
    D --> E["Optional: coherence or breathing dynamics"]
    E --> F["Record a short session"]
    F --> G["Check session.json + CSV + protocol.jsonl"]
    G --> H["Replay or review without hardware"]

    B -. if Windows blocks access .-> I["Use doctor / platform guide"]
    C -. if breathing is needed .-> J["Run breathing calibration"]
